<br>
It is OK Tiwgy, I am getting bored with this game anyways. I grow weery of all the Albs trying to tell everyone else how their class should not get this and that. I guess if you cannot win on the battlefield, you win in the Nerf War. No worries, let's see how much fun you have when there is nobody left to fight. Keep up the good work Tiwgy. Really keep it up. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/ukraq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KraQ</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_greenspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/3/02 11:13:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3657.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Assassin Balance Revisted:</span><hr size=1> sorry im a bit confused you mean 3 targets agains alb right? cuz chain (or scale) is the most common armor type in the game.<br>
