If you trained DW to 10, you would have roughly 350 spec pts to put into other places. There was several tests done by Elaa and someone else whose name I forgot (I think Drunkenkay maybe) showed that 10 DW/CD was better than 34 LA as far as base damage goes. Of course, LA style damage is better but then again that probably evens out the style damage and benefits of 50 Thrust (versus 34 or 39 slash for the SB). Those 350 spec pts turn into quicker access to higher level poisons, more stealth, allowing more items that boost CS or more CS.<br>
